dct_description_sm: Shows ecclesiastical boundaries. Includes graph of church membership. Illustrations of churches and cathedrals surround map. "III." In upper margin: Atlas pintoresco. From: García Cubas, Antonio, 1832-1912. Atlas pintoresco e histórico de los Estados Unidos Mexicanos. México : Debray Sucesores, 1885. (pl. III.).
